                    <h2 class="section-title">Our Culture</h2>
                    <p class="culture-description">
                        At Nihongo Sekai, we embrace the Japanese concept of
                        <em>Kaizen</em> - continuous improvement. Our culture is built
                        on respect, excellence, and the belief that learning is a
                        lifelong journey.
                    </p>

